      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ 395°F/ Gas 6</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Slice a few rings from the<strong> green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> and finely dice the rest</p><p>Tip: Deseed if you can't handle the heat!</p>",
