    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>crushed tomatillos</strong>, <strong>juice </strong>of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lime</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>diced green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>tomatillo salsa</strong></p>",
